{"tid":585392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣 都係一個好鐘意扮好人既撚樣?","createTime":"2018-03-08T15:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T15:57:08.000Z","uid":68626,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47e5efc03664854edf272409e752859f90863632","tid":585392,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"平時日日係到扮花生友扮無辜咩都唔關自己事<br />\n但係其實最鐘意見到人地勾心鬥角<br />\n同時永遠都唔會做任何衝突之中既主角<br />\n日日係挑撥離間之中生活<br />\n得閒幫下D 唔受歡迎/被杯葛既好人<br />\n目的只係為左樹立我好人既形象/唔想做醜人<br />\n但係又會參與講人壞話呢D環節<br />\n講完之後轉個頭再扮無辜報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6781fc24ec9390df4ed5d77c3666af0bb7ff455","tid":585392,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"廢柴 食塞米 扮曬蟹嘅屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"79c1c82e66702f2cfe84be76651d25dba3d6e6ca","tid":585392,"uid":102850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d2c46395e79971f8d4177b02d0e6eecbaf298c","tid":585392,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時日日係到扮花生友扮無辜咩都唔關自己事<br />\n但係其實最鐘意見到人地勾心鬥角<br />\n同時永遠都唔會做任何衝突之中既主角<br />\n日日係挑撥離間之中生活<br />\n得閒幫下D 唔受歡迎/被杯葛既好人<br />\n目的只係為左樹立我好人既形象/唔想做醜人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係又會參與講人壞話呢D環節<br />\n講完之後轉個頭再扮無辜報串</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得詭辯家, 即係樓主, 成日出引戰po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}